00Z","msg":"protein唔夠呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"呢排做咗紙板人<br />\n最近增肥中...<br />\n晚餐多咗碗昆布蛋花味噌湯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b979149e2aee31e278287641dd893275061db0","tid":2484974,"uid":272484,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"長期一日一餐（星期一至五） 星期六日唔理，想食就食，想飲就飲；唔會因為星期六日放綹左就肥返，唔洗擔心。<br />\n<br />\n要搞清楚既因果係Fasting 唔代表只為減肥，同時都會帶來好多健康既效果，除左Insulin resistance。<br />\n<br />\nFasting 最滿意既係唔會感覺到肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同時無糖低碳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49703c972f5f82670e0d73072760f507e860307c","tid":2484974,"uid":145635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:51:10.000Z","msg":"最近開始左幾日168,建議睇youtube既宋醫師了解下。佢唔只理論，佢自己都執行左成2年，講得好詳細同佢始終係醫生可信d,<br />\n<br />\n查左少少資料發覺好多youtuber 都係9吹，唔知係咪心理作用個人好似健康左，朝早精神d,但一來時間仲短2來我工作關係長期食外賣冇得特別注意咩2份菜1份肉1份穀咁，唔係應該效果更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最要留意既地方係進食時間內都唔可以食太少同太多，油既同垃圾食物都係可免則免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人意見"},{"pid":"78827e81522665917f6df224ae9424a6eff5ef6d","tid":2484974,"uid":230911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f29c27724a5139aa7db9c6fcd29ac20cd4a57068","tid":2484974,"uid":105678,"like":7,"dislike":23,"score":-16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T03:17:08.000Z","msg":"斷食係降低卡路里攝取嘅手段，其他成效都只係side effects<br />\n<br />\n如果目標係減肥，可以一用，不過做到嚴格抵制營養，唔需要特登去斷<br />\n<br />\n利：cut嗰陣會斷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:04:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QuZlPRrb8FM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQuZlPRrb8FM&d=WFG5iCHEkkmufTvr7zh8K0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=c1d13890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QuZlPRrb8FM</a><br />\n聽完科學家講斷食又好唔同"},{"pi