食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f600c5c3458fab66c394767137dc0f113e44734","tid":2484974,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9e38281bb1958aef789c6c524a24a612e4ba537","tid":2484974,"uid":331821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:13:45.000Z","msg":"一個禮拜抽一日唔食嘢廿零個鐘 (包括瞓覺時間)<br />\n通常都係早午晚唔食，訓前引唔到口先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T11:40:23.000Z","msg":"訓前忍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食杯水囉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eab1c3d26c644a4648b9300c9210d13a4c26aaa","tid":2484974,"uid":188374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c672476970859eab2192faad0be8961ea5ebd761","tid":2484974,"uid":275698,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"好多人將斷食=減肥<br />\n唔講討論一樣野首先基本了解一下，唔明可以問但最起碼唔好亂放fake news<br />\n<br />\n荷爾蒙有分同化 / 異化，例如血清素係代表清醒而褪黑色素係代表睡眠，兩者係一對咁去控制住個狀態<br />\n胰島素對應既係高血糖素，胰島素代表進食+吸收，高血營素代表消耗（大概意思）<br />\n<br />\n身體一分泌胰島素就會stop左脂肪細胞輸出脂肪既路徑，身體原本應該做既清理自噬反應（異化）就會轉向生長（同化）<br />\n<br />\n所以唔係講總熱量幾多，一直都冇提過要節食，減肥都唔係主要目的，而係斷食後修復新陳代謝修復飽肚感之後既自然結果<br />\n<br />\n成日只識講tdee，唔通一日訓覺4x 2h = 1x 8h咩，腦波深層睡眠快速眼動期呢啲自己google啦，根本成個身體狀態唔同晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:02:22.000Z","msg":"啲gym撚仲好撚串放圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜乜減肥法x 熱量赤字✓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連斷食有咩用都唔知，係度話斷食=食小左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abcf785b4dd91580602ab76acf0408f8c1dd140e","tid":2484974,"uid":188374,"like":1,"disl